id: pm-uzty
title: Fix Windows Nightly smoke cleanup helper import
description: "Nightly Validation run 27192052551 failed on windows-latest Node 20 while loading tests/integration/smoke-pack-cleanup.integration.spec.ts with SyntaxError. Duplicate check found only closed pm-i2xg for ENOTEMPTY cleanup behavior and open pm-ehbb for alerting, not this import-safety failure. Extract cleanupTempRoot into an import-safe smoke-cleanup module and keep the executable smoke script as the pack runner."
type: Issue
status: closed
priority: 2
tags[3]: "area:ci","area:release",windows
created_at: "2026-06-09T15:57:31.721Z"
updated_at: "2026-06-09T16:57:59.254Z"
author: codex-impl-20260609
parent: pm-u9d0
resolution: Extracted smoke cleanup logic into an import-safe helper module and updated the cleanup regression test to import that helper.
expected_result: Windows Nightly can load the packed smoke cleanup test without parsing the executable smoke runner during suite setup.
actual_result: tests/integration/smoke-pack-cleanup.integration.spec.ts imports scripts/smoke-cleanup.mjs; scripts/smoke-npx-from-pack.mjs still uses the same cleanup helper for pack smoke cleanup.
comments[6]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-06-09T16:02:01.593Z",codex-impl-20260609,"Evidence: fixed GitHub Nightly Validation run 27192052551 failure path by extracting cleanupTempRoot from executable scripts/smoke-npx-from-pack.mjs into import-safe scripts/smoke-cleanup.mjs and updating the smoke cleanup test import. Verification passed: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/integration/smoke-pack-cleanup.integration.spec.ts; npx -y node@20 node_modules/vitest/vitest.mjs run tests/integration/smoke-pack-cleanup.integration.spec.ts; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/integration/smoke-pack-cleanup.integration.spec.ts tests/unit/extension-loader.spec.ts tests/unit/sdk-index.spec.ts; node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage => 2606 tests, 100% statements/branches/functions/lines; pnpm build/typecheck/quality:static/contracts:check/changelog:pm:check/security:scan/audit moderate; manual isolated temp smoke passed."
  "2026-06-09T16:10:26.296Z",codex-impl-20260609,"Review follow-up: Gemini suggested treating EACCES as retryable for Windows cleanup locks. Applied to scripts/smoke-cleanup.mjs alongside ENOTEMPTY/EBUSY/EPERM; focused cleanup tests rerun before push."
  "2026-06-09T16:17:38.229Z",codex-impl-20260609,"Review polish: CodeRabbit suggested restoring the cleanup helper's first-level-entry removal comment after extraction. Restored the comment in scripts/smoke-cleanup.mjs; focused cleanup tests rerun before push."
  "2026-06-09T16:31:04.316Z",codex-impl-20260609,"Review follow-up: Gemini flagged Atomics.wait in the synchronous cleanup retry delay. Replaced it with a short busy-wait loop suitable for this standalone smoke cleanup helper; focused cleanup tests rerun before push."
  "2026-06-09T16:38:32.147Z",codex-impl-20260609,"Review follow-up: Gemini suggested avoiding CPU spin in the synchronous cleanup retry delay. Replaced busy wait with spawnSync(process.execPath, ['-e', setTimeout...]) and reran focused cleanup tests."
  "2026-06-09T16:57:59.254Z",codex-impl-20260609,"Review follow-up: Gemini flagged child-process sleep overhead in smoke cleanup retries. Verified local Node supports Atomics.wait synchronous sleep, replaced spawnSync sleep with Atomics.wait, and reran node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/integration/smoke-pack-cleanup.integration.spec.ts plus pnpm build and pnpm quality:static."
